            <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i></div><h3>Real-Time Analytics</h3><p>Experience real-time visitor analytics with custom reports. Track peak hours, visitor frequency, and security metrics.</p></div>
            <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-id-card"></i></div><h3>Digital Badges</h3><p>Generate professional visitor badges instantly with customizable templates, including photo capture and QR codes.</p></div>
            <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-bell"></i></div><h3>Instant Notifications</h3><p>Automatically notify hosts via email or SMS when their guest arrives, reducing wait times and improving experience.</p></div>
            <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i></div><h3>Security Compliance</h3><p>NDA signing, photo capture, and visitor logs ensure complete security and audit compliance for your organization.</p></div>
            <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-cloud-upload-alt"></i></div><h3>Cloud-Based Access</h3><p>Access your visitor data anywhere, anytime with secure cloud synchronization across multiple locations.</p></div>
